videos.description: West Virginia's defense falls for the fake, allowing Dru Brown to hit a wide-open Jelani Woods with a one-yard pass for an Oklahoma State touchdown.

videos.headline: Woods scores wide-open TD for OSU

videos.description: Jarret Doege sends a long pass to George Campbell, who runs in the touchdown to put West Virginia up 10-7.
